					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13837805#post-4805147</guid>
				<title>This article is truly unbearable</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13837805/scp-5464#post-4805147</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 27 Oct 2020 08:11:40 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Ralliston</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5986843</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>To quote a classic:<br /></p> <div style="text-align: center;"> <blockquote> <p>ME: &quot;Trick or bear?&quot;<br /> NEIGHBOR: &quot;Bear?&quot;<br /> ME: &quot;HE HAS CHOSEN THE BEAR!&quot;<br /> [distant roar and sounds of clanking chains]<br /> - <a href="https://twitter.com/rolldiggity">Matt Roller</a></p> </blockquote> </div> <hr /> <p>Anyway, this is stupid. This is beyond stupid. And it is supposed to be stupid.</p> <p>The whole thing started as an inside joke between me, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakob17" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5884163&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="Jakob17" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5884163)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jakob17" >Jakob17</a></span> on the SCPD Discord server. Though I usually don't really like articles that sprung out of stupid jokes, I just couldn't resist the urge to write this one.</p> <p>Special thanks to these folks for critting this absolute monstrosity:<br /> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6030962&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="Veralta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6030962)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veralta" >Veralta</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5903100&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="Pedagon" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5903100)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/pedagon" >Pedagon</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6394107&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="chiifu" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6394107)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chiifu" >chiifu</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3938622&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="The Great Hippo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3938622)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-great-hippo" >The Great Hippo</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/radioactiverads" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5053587&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="RadioactiveRADS" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5053587)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/radioactiverads" >RadioactiveRADS</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/itsdenali" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4284264&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="ItsDenali" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4284264)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/itsdenali" >ItsDenali</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wizzblizz" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6760712&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="WizzBlizz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6760712)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/wizzblizz" >WizzBlizz</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3242824&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="The Pighead" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3242824)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-pighead" >The Pighead</a></span> | <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/j-dune" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6682213&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="J Dune" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6682213)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/j-dune" >J Dune</a></span></p> <p><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">The punctuation mistakes in the message at the end are intentional, please DO NOT change them.</span></strong></p> <p>The Department of Ontokinetics logo used in the header was created by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609166659" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span> for the purpose of all articles regarding such. Please check out more of their absolutely stellar work <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/desk-of-junior-designer-s-yvonne">here</a>.</p> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">►&nbsp;Image&nbsp;sources</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;please&nbsp;don't&nbsp;sue&nbsp;me</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <blockquote> <p><strong>Name of the file:</strong> wojtek<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <strong>Source:</strong> <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Wojtek_the_bear.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Wojtek_the_bear.jpg</a><br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <strong>License:</strong> Open Data Commons Open Database License (ODbL)<br /> <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br /> <strong>Author:</strong> Imperial War Museum</p> </blockquote> </div> </div> </div> <div class="collapsible-block"> <div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">►&nbsp;Edits</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none"> <div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">▼&nbsp;also&nbsp;known&nbsp;as&nbsp;me&nbsp;getting&nbsp;touchy</a></div> <div class="collapsible-block-content"> <p><strong>Edit:</strong> +20 in seven hours?! That’s my personal best, thanks y’all &lt;3</p> <p><strong>Edit 2:</strong> +30 in ten hours. What. The. Actual. Hell.</p> <p><strong>Edit 3:</strong> +40 in a day. I physically cannot stress enough how this feels. I’ve been writing for four months now, not even dreaming of anything getting into the 30s. Yet, here I am, with a +40 article in a single day. Thank you all so much. It means a lot.</p> <p><strong>Edit 4:</strong> The Bear is now translated into <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-5464">Chinese</a>. This&#8230; this feels unreal.</p> <p><strong>Edit 5:</strong> +50 🥂. I've never gotten this far with anything. Thank you all so much.</p> <p><strong>Edit 6:</strong> The Bear is now also translated into <a href="http://scp-wiki.net.pl/scp-5464">Polish</a>. Should’ve seen this one coming :p.</p> <p><strong>Edit 7:</strong> +60. I am speechless.</p> <p><strong>Edit 8:</strong> +70. This has no interest in being so highly rated 0_0</p> <p><strong>Edit 9:</strong> +100. Jesus. What the hell. I&#8230; I never thought I'd get this far. I&#8230; thank you. From the bottom of my heart, thank you. &lt;3</p> </div> </div> </div> <hr /> <div style="text-align: center;"> <h3><span>~ <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/ralliston-s-authorpage">also check out the ralliston coolpage funpage or I *will* steal all of your cookies</a> ~</span></h3> </div> <hr /> 
